parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The dim headlights can cause reduced visibility, increasing the risk of accidents, especially at night or in low-light conditions.
symptoms: Headlights are extremely dim
making it difficult to see the road ahead
requiring the use of high beams
which can be distracting to oncoming drivers
and causing visibility hazards.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The delamination of the headlight reflectors can cause the headlights to become dim, reducing visibility and increasing the risk of accidents.
symptoms: Headlights are dim
reflectors are delaminating
and the pattern of delamination matches that of the recall.
